cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper discusses resource discovery systems and the automatic classification of resource meta-information, which are topics related to information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), and databases (cs.DB). The use of mathematical methods and concept analysis also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
